      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Advertisements</h2>
        <p>
          Our service may display advertisements from third parties such as Google AdSense. 
          We are not responsible for the content of these advertisements. Clicking on ads 
          may take you to third-party websites with their own terms and privacy policies.
